      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Jonatan Pettersson</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:172px;\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03152085169762414586\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/0/0a/Jonatanpettersson.jpg\" width=\"170\" height=\"226\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Jonatanpettersson.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Jonatan Pettersson <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Jonatan Pettersson</b>,<br />\na Swedish computer scientist and <a href=\"/Java\" title=\"Java\">Java</a> developer. He is author of the chess engine <a href=\"/Mediocre\" title=\"Mediocre\">Mediocre</a>, written in Java <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, \nand maintains the <i>Mediocre Chess blog</i>, covering the development of his engine and various topics on chess programming, also recently announcing he is working on a new <a href=\"/Bitboards\" title=\"Bitboards\">bitboard</a> based Java engine <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jonatan_Pettersson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=40671\">Blog back on track (Mediocre engine)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jonatan Pettersson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 07, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=40849\">Key collision handling</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jonatan Pettersson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 21, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table#Collisions\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Collisions</a>, <a href=\"/Zobrist_Hashing\" title=\"Zobrist Hashing\">Zobrist Hashing</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=41223\">Mediocre v0.4 released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jonatan Pettersson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 26, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=44633\">Mediocre v0.5 released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jonatan Pettersson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 30, 2012</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jonatan_Pettersson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://mediocrechess.blogspot.com/\">Mediocre Chess blog</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://mediocrechess.blogspot.com/2006/12/0x88-representation.html\">The 0x88 representation</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/0x88\" title=\"0x88\">0x88</a></dd>\n<dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://mediocrechess.blogspot.com/2007/01/guide-contempt-factor.html\">Contempt factor</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Contempt_Factor\" title=\"Contempt Factor\">Contempt Factor</a></dd>\n<dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://mediocrechess.blogspot.com/2007/03/guide-static-exchange-evaluation-see.html\">Static exchange evaluation (SEE)</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Static_Exchange_Evaluation\" title=\"Static Exchange Evaluation\">Static Exchange Evaluation</a></dd>\n<dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://mediocrechess.blogspot.com/2011/10/guide-tapered-eval.html\">Tapered Eval</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Tapered_Eval\" title=\"Tapered Eval\">Tapered Eval</a></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jonatan_Pettersson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03152085169762414586\">Blogger: Jonatan Pettersson</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://mediocrechess.sourceforge.net/\">Mediocre website</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://mediocrechess.blogspot.com/2019/03/info-still-around.html\">Still around, Mediocre Chess blog</a>, March 13, 2019</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301124316\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.012 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.014 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 57/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 130/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\n